"This desk reference is intended for the busy practitioner who needs a ready guide to basic information about the laws that affect intellectual property protection and transactions throughout the world. The essays which make up the Desk Reference are designed with readability and quick usage in mind. Section headings in a typical essay format include: treaties, patents, industrial designs and models, copyrights, trademarks, trade secrets and licensing. Contributions have been written by members of the worldwide lawyers network Lex Mundi."
